  <h1 class="page-title">About NeonGadgets</h1>
  <div class="about-content">
    <p>NeonGadgets was born from a fusion of two passions: cutting-edge technology and the timeless, vibrant glow of neon. We believe that the tools and toys we use every day shouldn't just be functional—they should be inspiring pieces of art.</p>
    <p>Founded in 2023, our mission has been to design and create high-quality electronic gadgets that stand out. From the click of a keyboard to the sound from your headphones, we want to elevate every interaction with a touch of neon brilliance.</p>
    <p>Our team is composed of designers, engineers, and enthusiasts who share a common vision. We spend our days experimenting with new materials and technologies to bring you products that are both beautiful and built to last. Thank you for being a part of our journey.</p>
  </div>
